OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FThe UK's Eurovision entrant Look Mum
OL,7,FNo Computer has performed his
OL,8,Feccentric song Eins, Zwei, Drei at the
OL,9,Flive final in Vienna in an evening
OL,10,Fthat mixed pop music and protest.
OL,12,FLook Mum No Computer, real name Sam
OL,13,FBattle, performed while wearing a pink
OL,14,Fjumpsuit and dancing energetically
OL,15,Fwith people dressed as fluffy green
OL,16,Fcomputers at the Wiener Stadthalle
OL,17,Farena on Saturday evening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
