OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FBattle, a YouTube star, moved around a
OL,7,Fmock workshop on the stage and at one
OL,8,Fpoint attempted to get the crowd to
OL,9,Fsing with him, chanting: "When I say
OL,10,Feins, you say zwei".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FHis act came in the middle of the
OL,18,FEurovision Song Contest, which went
OL,19,Fsmoothly despite months of calls for
OL,20,FIsrael to be excluded from the contest
OL,21,Fover its conflicts in Gaza and Lebanon.
OL,26,@qD@ZOU
