PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FIreland, Iceland, the Netherlands,
OL,7,FSpain and Slovenia all boycotted
OL,8,FEurovision this year.
OL,10,FProtesters demonstrated near the arena
OL,11,Fahead of the final, with the largest
OL,12,Fdemonstration No Stage For Genocide
OL,13,Fevent, organised by Palestine
OL,14,FSolidarity Austria, taking place at a
OL,15,Fplaypark on the outskirts of Vienna.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FThere was also a march from the city's
OL,7,Fwestern train station to the area
OL,8,Fwhere the Wiener Stadthalle is located
OL,9,Fon Saturday, but police directed
OL,10,Fprotesters away from the venue in a
OL,11,Floop.
OL,13,FOne demonstrator said it was
OL,14,F"important to protest against that
OL,15,Fidea that the song contest is not
OL,16,Fpolitical", declaring that the
OL,17,Fcompetition is "a very political
OL,18,Fevent".
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
