PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FGreece's act Akylas also attracted
OL,7,Fhuge amounts of attention online with
OL,8,Fhis video game-inspired performance of
OL,9,Fhis song Ferto, which involved him
OL,10,Fscootering along the stage in a tiger
OL,11,Fprint outfit.
OL,13,FFormer Love Island contestant Antigoni
OL,14,FBuxton, who was born in London,
OL,15,Fdelivered her song Jalla for Cyprus,
OL,16,Fwith hands reaching up from the stage
OL,17,Fbelow her and flames shooting out from
OL,18,Fbehind.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
