OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FDaniel Zizka, representing Czech
OL,7,FRepublic, appeared to be plagued by
OL,8,Ftechnical difficulties during his
OL,9,Fperformance of the song Crossroads,
OL,10,Fwhere he appeared inside an elaborate
OL,11,Fhall of mirrors.
OL,13,FAt one point the picture became
OL,14,Fdistorted and seemed to freeze as he
OL,15,Fsang, which UK commentator Graham
OL,16,FNorton said had not happened in
OL,17,Frehearsals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
