PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778976177
OL,3,CUK gives eccentric Eurovision
OL,4,Cperformance as Israel draws protest
OL,6,FLithuania's Lion Ceccah also gave an
OL,7,Feye-catching performance with his head
OL,8,Fand hands painted silver and a black
OL,9,Fsculpture-like costume.
OL,11,FA tear appeared to run down his face
OL,12,Fas he sang an emotional rendition of
OL,13,FSolo Quiero Mas before saying: "Thank
OL,14,Fyou Europe and humanity. I love you."
